      <title>Canada Goose 将削减 17% 的企业员工以削减成本</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/canada-goose-reduce-17-corporate-workforce-2024-03-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[豪华派克大衣制造商加拿大鹅 (Canada Goose) 周二表示，该公司将在全球裁员约 17%，这是在美国对高端商品的需求仍然面临压力之际控制成本的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/canada-goose-reduce-17-corporate-workforce-2024-03-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 13:26:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
